<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Posseken, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zum Rotemperg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns <add>nu</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schriben</expan> und der <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        lewt von Cappell und von Göring, die ewch <expan>zu
                            v<ex>er</ex>sprechen</expan> süllen steen, drey benennet habt etc., das
                        haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu ewch <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        Herlin, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen haben, mit ew
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu reden; und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> mal von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
